features.name: PNP_UDP_1 Catalyzes the reversible phosphorylytic cleavage of uridine and deoxyuridine to uracil and ribose- or deoxyribose-1- phosphate. The produced molecules are then utilized as carbon and energy sources or in the rescue of pyrimidine bases for nucleotide synthesis
AbiEii Nucleotidyl transferase AbiEii toxin, Type IV TA system
Radical_SAM Specifically methylates position 8 of adenine 2503 in 23S rRNA. Confers resistance to some classes of antibiotics
